    "feedback.privacy_desc": { en: "Your feedback is kept confidential and used only to improve our services.", sw: "Maoni yako huhifadhiwa kwa faragha na hutumika tu kuboresha huduma zetu.", ha: "Ra'ayin ka ana ajiye a sirri kuma ana amfani da kawai don inganta hidimomin mu.", yo: "Im yo r j p n t n wa l t n.", ig: "R g g ejide n'ime nzuzo ma j na-eji ya melu or r g any.", zu: "Isipho sakho sihlala sihlanganiswe kwaye sisetyenziselwa ukuthuthukisa iinkonzo zethu kuphela.", xh: "Isipho sakho sihlala sihlanganiswe kwaye sisetyenziselwa ukuthuthukisa iinkonzo zethu kuphela.", af: "Jou terugvoer word vertroulik gehou en slegs gebruik om ons dienste te verbeter.", tw: "Nkyerkyer mu wo y p n.", rw: "Ibyanditswe byawe bihifuzwa kandi bikakoreshwa gusa ku guhindura imikorere yacu.", lg: "Ebiwandiiko byo bibika bya bulungi era bikozesebwa kukulondoola emirimu gyaffe.", fr: "Vos commentaires sont gardés confidentiels et utilisés uniquement pour améliorer nos services.", dy: "A bii kunnafoni" },

